# Cookie和Session

## Cookie简介

Cookie就是客户端存储技术，以**键值对**的形式存在。

在B/S架构中，服务器端产生Cookie响应给客户端，浏览器接收后把Cookie存在在指定的文件夹中，以后每次请求浏览器都会把Cookie内容放入到请求中。

## Go语言对Cookie的支持

```go
type Cookie struct {
    Name   string		//Cookie的名字
    Value  string		//Cookie的值
    Quoted bool // indicates whether the Value was originally quoted

    Path       string    // optional	有效范围
    Domain     string    // optional	可访问Cookie的域
    Expires    time.Time // optional	过期时间
    RawExpires string    // for reading cookies only

    // MaxAge=0 means no 'Max-Age' attribute specified.
    // MaxAge<0 means delete cookie now, equivalently 'Max-Age: 0'
    // MaxAge>0 means Max-Age attribute present and given in seconds
    MaxAge      int		//最大存活时间
    Secure      bool
    HttpOnly    bool	//是否可以通过脚本访问
    SameSite    SameSite
    Partitioned bool
    Raw         string
    Unparsed    []string // Raw text of unparsed attribute-value pairs
}
```

## Go操作Cookie

```go
func welcome(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {
    t, _ := template.ParseFiles("view/cookietest.gohtml")
    t.Execute(w, nil)
}
func setCookie(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {
	c := http.Cookie{Name: "myname", Value: "myvalue"}
	http.SetCookie(w, &c)	//设置到响应头
	t, _ := template.ParseFiles("view/cookietest.gohtml")
	t.Execute(w, nil)
}

func getCookie(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {
	cs := r.Cookies()	//遍历得到Cookie的全部键值对
	t, _ := template.ParseFiles("view/cookietest.gohtml")
	t.Execute(w, cs)	//传给模版
}

func main() {
	http.HandleFunc("/", welcome)
	http.HandleFunc("/setCookie", setCookie)
	http.HandleFunc("/getCookie", getCookie)
	http.ListenAndServe(":9090", nil)
}
